This Project is divided into two Modules 
1-  User Management ->
        Features under UM  are
            1. Register
            2. Signin
            3. Sign out

2- Contact Management-
    1. Show Contact
    2. Update Contact
    3. Add Contact
    4. Search Contact (Optional)

Technology USED ----
______________________________________

SpringBoot
Modules- 
  1. Spring MVC
  2.Thymeleaf
  3. JPA - Hibernate
  4.Spring Security

DataBase - MYSQL
